        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21575078-florencia?shelf=religions-myths-and-other-stories">religions-myths-and-other-stories</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21575078-florencia?shelf=philosophyland">philosophyland</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21575078-florencia?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>
          </div>
