        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1899221036" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7762909959228255460">I think I had admittedly underrated Russell until reading this. A wonderful example of forward thinking, and his influence can be clearly recognised in the works of contemporary thinkers (particularly Sam Harris&apos; views of morality and Christopher Hitchens&apos; linkage of Stalinism and state religiosity). Definitely worth reading.</span>
  <span id="freeText7762909959228255460" style="display:none">I think I had admittedly underrated Russell until reading this. A wonderful example of forward thinking, and his influence can be clearly recognised in the works of contemporary thinkers (particularly Sam Harris' views of morality and Christopher Hitchens' linkage of Stalinism and state religiosity). Definitely worth reading.</span>
